
The following files provide basic utilities for nodal Legendre spectral methods

deriv_mat.m
gen_eig_decomp.m
hdr.m
interp_mat.m
kron3.m
semhat.m
tensor2.m
tensor3.m
zwgl.m
zwglc.m
zwgll.m
zwuni.m



SYNOPSIS:

Useful formatting shortcuts

   hdr.m

Generate sets of points and weights:

   zwgll.m           Gauss-Lobatto-Legendre points and weights
   zwuni.m           Uniform points and weights
   zwgl.m            Gauss-Legendre points and weights
   zwglc.m           Gauss-Lobatto-Chebyshev points and weights

Polynomial interpolation / derivative matrices

   interp_mat(zo,z)  J_ij =  l_j(r_i), where r_i is not one of the nodal points
   deriv_mat.m       D_ij =  dl_j/dx at nodes x_i, where l_j(x_i) = delta_ij

One-dimensional SEM matrices of order N: Ah, Bh, Ch, Dh, z, w

   semhat.m

Provide generalized eigendecomposition for A=A' and SPD B, such that
eigenvectors are orthonormal in the B inner-product

   gen_eig_decomp.m

Generate a Kronecker product AxBxC

   kron3.m

Evaluate Kronecker product x vector:  w = (AxBxC)v (do not form AxBxC).

   tensor3.m

Evaluate Kronecker product x vector:  w = (AxB)v 

   tensor2.m


